OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781869673
OL,3,CInquest opened and suspended into
OL,4,Cdeath of great-grandmother in Cleator
OL,5,CMoor
OL,7,FAn inquest has been opened and
OL,8,Fsuspended into the death of a great-
OL,9,Fgrandmother who died after she was
OL,10,Fstruck by a motorbike close to her
OL,11,FCleator Moor home.
OL,13,FCumbria Coroner's Court, sitting in
OL,14,FWorkington, heard on Tuesday 16 June
OL,15,Fhow 75-year-old Gillian Moreen
OL,16,FLivingstone, of Ennerdale Road, lost
OL,17,Fher life after she suffered
OL,18,F"significant injuries" in a collision
OL,19,Fwhich occurred while she was crossing
OL,20,Fthe road with a grandchild.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
