FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781869673
OL,3,CInquest opened and suspended into
OL,4,Cdeath of great-grandmother in Cleator
OL,5,CMoor
OL,7,FBorn in Pretoria, South Africa, Mrs
OL,8,FLivingstone was a retired bank worker
OL,9,Fwho was married to David, a retired
OL,10,Fchief technician.
OL,12,FMrs Livingstone died at the scene of
OL,13,Fthe collision, on Ennerdale Road,
OL,14,Fwhich occurred at around 4.25pm on
OL,15,FTuesday 26 May.
OL,17,FCoroner Ms Margaret Taylor formally
OL,18,Fopened the inquest into her death, and
OL,19,Fsaid: "Due to ongoing police
OL,20,Fenquiries, I am suspending the inquest
OL,21,Finto Mrs Gillian Livingstone's death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781869673
OL,3,CInquest opened and suspended into
OL,4,Cdeath of great-grandmother in Cleator
OL,5,CMoor
OL,7,F"A decision upon resumption will be
OL,8,Fmade following the completion of
OL,9,Fpolice enquiries."
OL,11,FThe grandchild was taken to hospital
OL,12,Fhaving suffered a serious head injury.
OL,14,FIn a tribute to Mrs Livingstone,
OL,15,Frelatives described the mother,
OL,16,Fgrandmother and great grandmother as
OL,17,Fthe "matriarch of the family".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
