OL,3,CInquest opened and suspended into
OL,4,Cdeath of great-grandmother in Cleator
OL,5,CMoor
OL,7,FThe family said: "She was the focal
OL,8,Fpoint for information, guidance,
OL,9,Fadvice and caring. She will be greatly
OL,10,Fmissed by the whole family and leaves
OL,11,Fa huge void to fill."
